OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA warm or very warm day with
OL,6,Flight winds and plenty of sunshine for
OL,7,Fmost. Feeling a little cooler along
OL,8,Fthe coast with the sea breeze.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry and settled evening
OL,11,Fwith clear skies across the whole
OL,12,Fregion. Winds will be light and
OL,13,Fvariable. Remaining mild overnight.
OL,14,
OL,15,CMonday:FA sunny and hot day across the
OL,16,Fregion with clear skies and light and
OL,17,Fvariable winds.
