OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTemperature may start to slowly
OL,7,Fdecrease on Tuesday and Wednesday but
OL,8,Fstill remaining above average for the
OL,9,Ftime of year. Thursday will be cloudy
OL,10,Fat times with occasional showers.
